# Repository formats discussion

What should we do for Darcs 2.8 with regards to the old-fashioned (OF)
repositories ?

Different options:

-   Keeping full OF support
-   Keeping all read-only support
-   Keeping only `darcs optimize --upgrade` support

The devil is in the details, there are in fact much more than 3 options,
we will probably discuss the behaviour of each command.

